+# Additional terms under GNU GPLv3 section 7
+
+Copyright © 2026 Myldy Design (`github.com/myldy20`).
+
+These terms apply only to first-party Cursed Drone material whose source file contains a notice referring to this document. They do not change the licences of third-party components listed in `THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md`.
+
+When conveying a modified version of covered first-party material, you must:
+
+1. preserve `NOTICE.md`, this file, and existing copyright and licence notices;
+2. include the following attribution in the modified project's README or in an About, Credits, or Legal Notices screen/file that is reasonably accessible to recipients:
+
+   > Based on Cursed Drone by Myldy Design — https://github.com/myldy20/cursed-drone
+
+3. clearly state that the version has been modified and is not an official Cursed Drone release unless Myldy Design has explicitly approved it.
+
+No rights are granted under trademark law to use the names **Cursed Drone** or **Myldy Design**, or their logos, as the name or branding of a modified distribution, or to imply endorsement by Myldy Design. Descriptive use of the names for the attribution above is permitted.
+
+These terms do not require an attribution splash screen, a logo in the working interface, or citations in videos, posts, papers, or other external publications.
